      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation (ANSYS Fluent 19.2) must be validated under an institutional SQA plan covering version control, regression testing, and documented release notes. Required level 2 mandates that the solver is a commercially released code with documented verification tests.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 19.2 is a commercially released CFD solver with documented regression test suites and release notes. Institutional SQA procedures including version control and access logging are in place. Required level 2 is satisfied."
    },
    {
