      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification must demonstrate that the solver correctly implements governing equations through method-of-manufactured-solutions or benchmark comparisons at required level 2. Published ANSYS Fluent benchmark results for laminar and turbulent internal flows must be cited.",
      "rationale": "Published ANSYS Fluent verification benchmarks for internal flow (ASME benchmark suite) confirm correct implementation of Navier-Stokes equations. Lid-driven cavity and pipe flow benchmarks reproduce analytical solutions to within 0.1%. Required level 2 is met."
    },
